      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;AC softcaps don't reduce the amount of visual AC you get from a buff. What they reduce is the effect the AC has. If I cast a 72ac buff on myself, it shows a 72 ac increase on my inventory screen. However, since I am over my softcap, the effect off that buff is more like 18 ac in terms of damage reduced.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Why your Ac buff is giving less than 72 ac is beyond me. Perhaps it is a stacking issue with Tribute, or something along those lines.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
